　10　　月　　26　　日\r\n                              書  記  官  林佳陞","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/110%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c1091%2c20211115%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,110,嘉簡,1091,20211115,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"1091","JDATE":"20211115","JTITLE":"竊盜"}